reviewText: basic AF. Some questions are worded strangely and that was the only part that was difficult.  Also there's no message at the end to make it clear you've finished the entire course, think there should be a recap of all the areas covered, maybe a general pack to download as a takeaway that combines all the resources provided, so you don't forget a week after you finished the course. One positive was that some of the information found elsewhere was well curated and useful, just surprised it was optional reading.
